title: Watch typescript changes
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

In order to watch for changes as you're developing, run `tsc --watch` or `tsc -w`

Some useful options:

* `--excludeDirectories` - by default excludes `node_modules` and some other package folders.
* `--excludeFiles` if only some files need to be excluded